<br>
Everfrost Rod:  Jump in the closest hole and stay as close to the frozen surface as you can and approach the wall that goes underneath.. right at the wall my head seemed to go above water for just a breath.. made it no problem.  This may be a glitch, but you never know.   Unrest rod.. easy.. get ivu and grab it <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> .  Oasis rod killed me, just swim up invis and hope they dont see you.. hopefully you can get your body to a recoverable spot  before you die &lt;grin&gt;  Rathe rod... Get a waterstone from a friendly mage and pray!! neriak rod.  invis and swim as much as you can, guards dont bug you down there, If you are a DE, you can actually grab the rod from inside the blind fish.. get right up on the window. &lt;same for enchanters with the coin&gt;  <br>
<br>
